title: The Comet Nemesis
description: Born 3 years after a super comet hits earth, Noah has a fascination with holographic technology developed by his genius mother. During research into his colonies holodeck technology, a power spike transports him, 65 years into the future.

title: Meeting with the Shadow Master
description: Trapped in North Col, Noah and Geneva attempt to prove they are telling the truth about time travel. Meanwhile the shadow master reveals himself as a time traveler. Sundance awakes from a fight with is brother by the ocean.

title: Lies and Secrets
description: Facing a 5 year sentence for lying after their attempt to prove time travel to the triumverate fails, Becky helps Noah and Geneva escape. Arushka and dolly search for sundance while the protectors prepare to activate the electronet.

title: Episode #3.1
description: The wormhole technology invented by Noah to allow travel through space and time is put to nefarious purposes by kids who kidnap his best friend.
